Package ohos.agp.render

Class Insets

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.render.Insets
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class Insets
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Provides a wrapper class representing the offsets for the left, top, right, and bottom bounds of a rectangle.

    A positive value indicates that the bound approaches the rectangle center, while a negative value indicates that the bound moves away from the rectangle center.

    Since:
    5
